@startuml BFS_Algorithm_Activity_Diagram
!theme plain
title ALRS v2 — BFS Citation Crawl Algorithm
caption Activity Diagram — GraphSearchService.run_full_search()

|#LightBlue| BFS Cycle |
|#LightGreen| Embedding |
|#LightYellow| Decision |

|BFS Cycle|
start
:Receive **queued_dois** list\nand session parameters;
note right
  Parameters:
  - session_id
  - seed_doi
  - research_questions
  - similarity_threshold
  - max_depth
  - mode (automated | interactive)
end note

:Emit **SEARCH_STARTED** event (0%);
:Embed research questions\n(GeminiService.embed_question);

|Decision|
:Initialize queue ← [seed_doi];

|BFS Cycle|
while (queue is not empty\nAND depth ≤ max_depth?) is (yes)

  :Pre-fetch existing session DOIs\nfrom Neo4j (get_session_dois);

  while (For each DOI in queue) is (next DOI)

    if (DOI already in session graph?) then (yes)
      :Skip DOI\n(already processed);
    else (no)

      :Rate-limit: **acquire** token\n(AdaptiveRateLimiter);

      :Fetch paper metadata\nfrom **OpenAlex**\n(get_paper_by_doi);

      if (Paper found?) then (yes)

        :MERGE Paper node\nin **Neo4j**\n(create_paper);

        :Link paper to session\nat current depth\n(link_paper_to_session);

        :Rate-limit: acquire token;
        :Fetch **citations** from OpenAlex\n(get_citations → citing DOIs);

        :Rate-limit: acquire token;
        :Fetch **references** from OpenAlex\n(get_references → referenced DOIs);

        while (For each neighbour DOI) is (next)
          :Create **stub** Paper node\nif not exists;
          :MERGE **CITES** edge\n(create_citation);
        endwhile (done)

        :Collect new DOIs\n(not yet in session);

      else (not found)
        :Log error:\n"Not found in OpenAlex";
      endif

    endif

  endwhile (all DOIs processed)

  :Emit **LEVEL_COMPLETE** event;
  :Return **CycleResult**\n{level, papers_discovered,\npapers_new, new_dois, errors};

  |Embedding|
  :Get unembedded DOIs\n(get_unembedded_dois);

  while (For each unembedded DOI) is (next DOI)

    if (has_embedding == true?) then (yes)
      :Skip (already embedded);
    else (no)

      :Fetch abstract\nfrom Neo4j\n(get_paper_abstract);

      if (Abstract exists?) then (yes)
        :Rate-limit: acquire token;
        :Call **Gemini** embed_paper\n(RETRIEVAL_DOCUMENT task type);
        :Store embedding vector\nin **Neo4j**\n(store_paper_embedding);
      else (no abstract)
        :Skip embedding;
      endif

    endif

  endwhile (done)

  :Emit **EMBEDDING_PROGRESS** event;

  |Decision|
  if (mode == automated?) then (automated)
    :queue ← cycle.new_dois\n(feed ALL new DOIs to next level);
    :depth++;
  else (interactive)
    :Emit **CYCLE_RESULTS** event\nwith level stats;
    :Set session status = PAUSED;
    :PAUSE — await user /enqueue;
    stop
  endif

endwhile (queue empty OR depth exceeded)

|Decision|
:Update session stats\n(update_session_stats);
:Emit **SEARCH_COMPLETE** event (100%);
stop

@enduml
